    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[BackdropUrl], [m].[Budget], [m].[CreatedBy], [m].[CreatedDate], [m].[ImdbUrl], [m].[OriginalLanguage], [m].[Overview], [m].[PosterUrl], [m].[Price], [m].[ReleaseDate], [m].[Revenue], [m].[Runtime], [m].[Tagline], [m].[Title], [m].[TmdbUrl], [m].[UpdatedBy], [m].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Movies] AS [m]
    INNER JOIN [MovieGenres] AS [m0] ON [m].[Id] = [m0].[MovieId]
    WHERE [m0].[GenreId] = @__id_0
    ORDER BY [m].[Revenue] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

SELECT DISTINCT [t].[Id], [t].[BackdropUrl], [t].[Budget], [t].[CreatedBy], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ImdbUrl], [t].[OriginalLanguage], [t].[Overview], [t].[PosterUrl], [t].[Price], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Revenue], [t].[Runtime], [t].[Tagline], [t].[Title], [t].[TmdbUrl], [t].[UpdatedBy], [t].[UpdatedDate]
FROM (
    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[BackdropUrl], [m].[Budget], [m].[CreatedBy], [m].[CreatedDate], [m].[ImdbUrl], [m].[OriginalLanguage], [m].[Overview], [m].[PosterUrl], [m].[Price], [m].[ReleaseDate], [m].[Revenue], [m].[Runtime], [m].[Tagline], [m].[Title], [m].[TmdbUrl], [m].[UpdatedBy], [m].[UpdatedDate]

SELECT DISTINCT [t].[Id], [t].[BackdropUrl], [t].[Budget], [t].[CreatedBy], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ImdbUrl], [t].[OriginalLanguage], [t].[Overview], [t].[PosterUrl], [t].[Price], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Revenue], [t].[Runtime], [t].[Tagline], [t].[Title], [t].[TmdbUrl], [t].[UpdatedBy], [t].[UpdatedDate]
FROM (
    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[BackdropUrl], [m].[Budget], [m].[CreatedBy], [m].[CreatedDate], [m].[ImdbUrl], [m].[OriginalLanguage], [m].[Overview], [m].[PosterUrl], [m].[Price], [m].[ReleaseDate], [m].[Revenue], [m].[Runtime], [m].[Tagline], [m].[Title], [m].[TmdbUrl], [m].[UpdatedBy], [m].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Movies] AS [m]
    INNER JOIN [MovieGenres] AS [m0] ON [m].[Id] = [m0].[MovieId]
    WHERE [m0].[GenreId] = @__id_0
    ORDER BY [m].[Revenue] DESC

    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[BackdropUrl], [m].[Budget], [m].[CreatedBy], [m].[CreatedDate], [m].[ImdbUrl], [m].[OriginalLanguage], [m].[Overview], [m].[PosterUrl], [m].[Price], [m].[ReleaseDate], [m].[Revenue], [m].[Runtime], [m].[Tagline], [m].[Title], [m].[TmdbUrl], [m].[UpdatedBy], [m].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Movies] AS [m]
    INNER JOIN [MovieGenres] AS [m0] ON [m].[Id] = [m0].[MovieId]
    WHERE [m0].[GenreId] = @__id_0
    ORDER BY [m].[Revenue] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
